nterfaith Organization Issues Guidelines for Religious Leaders to Pevent Sexual Offenses|url=https://forward.com/fast-forward/388907/interfaith-organization-issues-guidelines-for-religious-leaders-to-prevent/|publisher=Forward|accessdate=8 April 2018}}</ref> 

